# Job Tracker Project Structure

## Overview
This is a client-side job application tracking system built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The application is fully modular and works offline with local storage.

## File Organization

### Main Application Files
- [index.html](mdc:index.html) - Main HTML structure with authentication, job tracking, dashboard, and settings
- [styles.css](mdc:styles.css) - Complete application styling with dark theme and responsive design

### JavaScript Modules (js/ directory)

#### Core State Management
- [js/state-manager.js](mdc:js/state-manager.js) - Centralized state management with IndexedDB and event-driven updates
- [js/indexeddb-manager.js](mdc:js/indexeddb-manager.js) - IndexedDB operations and database management
- [js/localstorage-manager.js](mdc:js/localstorage-manager.js) - localStorage fallback manager
- [js/data.js](mdc:js/data.js) - Data utilities, validation, and storage abstraction layer

#### Application Core
- [js/app.js](mdc:js/app.js) - Application entry point, PWA installation, admin panel initialization
- [js/auth.js](mdc:js/auth.js) - Authentication management, password hashing, session control
- [js/job-tracker.js](mdc:js/job-tracker.js) - Core job CRUD operations and UI management
- [js/dashboard.js](mdc:js/dashboard.js) - Analytics dashboard, admin panel, Chart.js visualizations
- [js/settings.js](mdc:js/settings.js) - Custom statuses/stages, PWA installation preferences

#### Features & Utilities
- [js/csv.js](mdc:js/csv.js) - CSV import/export functionality with parsing and validation
- [js/weekly-report.js](mdc:js/weekly-report.js) - Weekly report generation and export
- [js/notifications.js](mdc:js/notifications.js) - Toast notification system
- [js/advanced-analytics.js](mdc:js/advanced-analytics.js) - Advanced export and analytics features
- [js/calendar-integration.js](mdc:js/calendar-integration.js) - Calendar sync and event management

#### PWA & Installation
- [js/cross-platform-detector.js](mdc:js/cross-platform-detector.js) - Cross-platform detection for PWA installation
- [js/install-analytics.js](mdc:js/install-analytics.js) - PWA installation analytics tracking
- [js/install-prompt-ui.js](mdc:js/install-prompt-ui.js) - Installation prompt UI components
- [js/pwa-install.js](mdc:js/pwa-install.js) - PWA installation manager and handlers

#### Testing & Debug
- [js/tests/](mdc:js/tests/) - Comprehensive test suite (10 test files)
- [debug-storage.html](mdc:debug-storage.html) - Storage debugging and inspection tool
- [test-state-management.html](mdc:test-state-management.html) - State management testing suite

### PWA & Service Worker
- [sw.js](mdc:sw.js) - Service Worker for offline functionality and caching
- [manifest.json](mdc:manifest.json) - PWA manifest for app installation and branding

### Test Files
- [test-admin-panel.html](mdc:test-admin-panel.html) - Complete admin panel functionality testing
- [test-pwa-integration-complete.html](mdc:test-pwa-integration-complete.html) - PWA integration testing
- [test-pwa-components.html](mdc:test-pwa-components.html) - PWA component unit tests
- [test-dashboard-integration.html](mdc:test-dashboard-integration.html) - Dashboard integration testing
- [test-cross-platform-detector.html](mdc:test-cross-platform-detector.html) - Cross-platform detection testing

### Documentation
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Project overview, features, and setup instructions
- [CONTRIBUTING.md](mdc:CONTRIBUTING.md) - Development guidelines and contribution process
- [CHANGELOG.md](mdc:CHANGELOG.md) - Version history and changes
- [LICENSE](mdc:LICENSE) - MIT license
- [sample_import.csv](mdc:sample_import.csv) - Sample CSV data for testing imports

## Architecture Principles
- **Modular Design**: Each feature in its own JavaScript file with clear separation of concerns
- **Centralized State Management**: Single source of truth with event-driven updates and IndexedDB persistence
- **Client-Side Only**: No backend, all data stored in IndexedDB with localStorage fallback
- **Accessibility First**: WCAG 2.1 AA compliance with semantic HTML, ARIA attributes, keyboard navigation
- **Mobile Responsive**: Mobile-first design approach with responsive admin panel
- **Security**: SHA-256 password hashing with Web Crypto API
- **PWA Ready**: Progressive Web App with offline functionality and installation analytics
- **Admin Panel**: Comprehensive admin panel with PWA installation analytics and management
- **Error Resilience**: Comprehensive error handling with graceful fallbacks and user feedback
- **Performance Optimized**: Efficient data operations with minimal redundant I/O
